locality: Hang Kia-Pa Co Nature Reserve. Mai Chau Distr., Pa Co Municipality, Pa Co Con village.

Distr. Lac Duong, municipality Da Chay, vicinity of Klong Lanh village, 31 km to NE of Dalat City. Secondary grasslands and shrub associations on river valley at foothills of W macroslope of Bi Dup mountain system.
